{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji46","name":"毛泽东全集第46卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji46.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给林铁的信和题词","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给林铁?的信和题词"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1963年11月17日）林铁同志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遵嘱写了几个字，不知是否可用？浪陶（淘）沙一词”，待后再写。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此祝康吉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十一月十七日一定要根治海河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六三年十一月十七日[1]林铁，当时任中共河北省委第一书记。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[2]指毛泽东应林铁要求为即将在天津举办的河北抗洪抢险斗争展览会写的题词。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[3]指毛泽东1954年夏写的词《浪淘沙·北戴河》。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":11,"day":17}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":93,"page_end":93},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}